      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are going through an incredibly painful time, and I am so sorry you are feeling this heavy burden of betrayal and emptiness. Please know that your feelings are valid, but you do not have to face this darkness alone. If you feel overwhelmed by these thoughts, reaching out to a trusted friend or a mental health professional can provide the support you desperately need.",
